            <h3>Imperial Tea Village in Darjeeling</h3>
            <p>Taba Kosi & Seven Tea Gardens in one place<br>
                & home stay accommodation in cottage.</p>
            <span><a href="{{ path('tea_homestay_pageview',{'id':1}) }}">know more</a></span>
        </div>
        <nav class="slides-navigation">
            <a href="#" class="next"></a>
            <a href="#" class="prev"></a>
